{"event_counts": {"item.completed": 11, "item.started": 6, "thread.started": 1, "turn.completed": 1, "turn.started": 1}, "last_agent_message": "Updated [cache.py](/var/folders/gc/8tw_jq1j09x5gsqhs1bc24cr0000gn/T/codex_benchmark_cache_invalidation_dependency_2073_kwsqjjqp/cache_invalidation_dependency_2073/cache.py) to keep dependency bookkeeping consistent when a node changes between derived and source.

